#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. Childless"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Appamādasutta"
msgstr "17. Diligence"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.195"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, King Pasenadi said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.4"
msgid "“atthi nu kho, bhante, eko dhammo yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“Sir, is there one thing that secures benefits for both"

msgctxt "sn3.17:1.5"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti?"
msgstr "the present life and lives to come?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:2.1"
msgid "“Atthi kho, mahārāja, eko dhammo yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“There is, great king.”"

msgctxt "sn3.17:2.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:3.1"
msgid "“Katamo pana, bhante, eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "“So what is it?”"

msgctxt "sn3.17:3.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.87"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Appamādo kho, mahārāja, eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr ""
"“Diligence, great king, is one thing that, when developed and cultivated, "
"secures benefits for both"

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.2"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcāti."
msgstr "the present life and lives to come."

#. VAR: jaṅgalānaṃ → jaṅgamānaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn3.17:4.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, yāni kānici jaṅgalānaṃ pāṇānaṃ padajātāni, sabbāni "
"tāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gacchanti, hatthipadaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati—"
"yadidaṃ mahantattena;"
msgstr ""
"The footprints of all creatures that walk can fit inside an elephant’s "
"footprint. So an elephant’s footprint is said to be the biggest of them all."

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.4"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, mahārāja, appamādo eko dhammo, yo ubho atthe samadhiggayha "
"tiṭṭhati—"
msgstr "In the same way, diligence is one thing that secures benefits for both"

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.5"
msgid "diṭṭhadhammikañceva atthaṃ samparāyikañcā”ti."
msgstr "the present life and lives to come.”"

msgctxt "sn3.17:4.6"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe …"
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. …"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.1"
msgid "“Āyuṃ arogiyaṃ vaṇṇaṃ,"
msgstr "“For one who desires a continuous flow"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.2"
msgid "saggaṃ uccākulīnataṃ;"
msgstr "of exceptional delights—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.3"
msgid "Ratiyo patthayantena,"
msgstr "long life, beauty, and health,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:5.4"
msgid "uḷārā aparāparā."
msgstr "heaven, and birth in an eminent family—"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.1"
msgid "Appamādaṃ pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "the astute praise diligence"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.2"
msgid "puññakiriyāsu paṇḍitā;"
msgstr "in making merit."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.3"
msgid "Appamatto ubho atthe,"
msgstr "Being diligent, an astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:6.4"
msgid "adhiggaṇhāti paṇḍito."
msgstr "secures both benefits:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.1"
msgid "Diṭṭhe dhamme ca yo attho,"
msgstr "the benefit in this life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.2"
msgid "yo cattho samparāyiko;"
msgstr "and in lives to come."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.3"
msgid "Atthābhisamayā dhīro,"
msgstr "A sage, comprehending the meaning,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.17:7.4"
msgid "paṇḍitoti pavuccatī”ti."
msgstr "is called ‘astute’.”"
